<h1>心</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">xīn</span><span class=alesi>(xin1)</span> , xin <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 心 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 心</h2><div class=abo>
